    <description>
        <p>
            Yet another Bilibili client.
        </p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Multilingual: Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese (automatic translation), English...</li>
            <li>Theme: support automatic switching of theme according to system settings</li>
            <li>Play page: video, bangumi, film and TV show</li>
            <li>Personal page: scan qrcode to login, history and Personal collection...</li>
            <li>Search page: hotspot, videos and bangumi...</li>
            <li>Activity page: recently updated video of the following uploader</li>
            <li>Live page: support watching the following uploader and other system recommendations</li>
            <li>Flatpak: wiliwili config directory is ~/.var/app/cn.xfangfang.wiliwili/config/wiliwili</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
